snippet.title: Anno 2205 Gamescom Recap [US]
snippet.description:
Build up huge cities and take off into space in Anno 2205. See the new region and brand-new feature revealed at gamescom.

Best Sim of E3 2015
—Neoseeker

Learn more at anno-game.ubi.com.
